{
  "stem": "4361.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was two nights-- two days and three nights of horror because there was no food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whatever food there was was eventually consumed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the thirst became awful, became dreadful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember particularly that thirst was the worst thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember as the train would stop, and while the train was still in Hungary, peasant women, Hungarian peasant women, would come out with pails of water and try to sell it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember I climbed-- because there was a little barred window-- climbed there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was showing a ring.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was ready to reach to give me the water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then an SS kicked the bucket, the pail.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it was still-- and it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But there was still a certain amount of-- of civilized behavior because there were two buckets there for sanitary purposes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So whenever somebody would have to use it, there was still some reluctance, some attempt at privacy by two people holding a blanket.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But it was foul.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It stunk.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Children crying-- my little niece, Eva, who was about four weeks old, the mother didn't have any more milk.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But still, we'll get to Kenyermezo, and then this misery is going to be over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Except that one night, a neighbor of ours, whom I knew by the name of Mr.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Weinfeld, who originally came from Poland, and who had the good sense at the time the Hungarians marched in, to make sure he had Hungarian citizenship-- although what difference it made-- by now, I really realize that it made none.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He said one night in Yiddish, [SPEAKING YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They looked at him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What are you talking about?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are going to Kenyermezo.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can smell the Tatra air.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
